abstract: "Repository package for a conservative cancer-informatics evidence synthesis of C1Q/SPP1 macrophage-associated spatial context in public NSCLC resources. The repository provides manuscript files, figures, processed source-data tables, and traceability documentation; it is not a clinical implementation or treatment-selection tool."
keywords:
  - cancer informatics
  - NSCLC
  - C1Q
  - SPP1
  - macrophage context
  - spatial transcriptomics
  - reproducibility
